d in the April 2007 massacre at Virginia Tech:</p><p>Bloomberg said that copies of all the videos would be sent to every member of the incoming 113th congress.</p><p>Referring to <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/dec/14/newtown-shooting-quiet-town-shooting\">the shootings in Newtown</a>, Connecticut on Friday, Bloomberg said \"if this moment passes into memory without action from Washington, it will be a stain\" on the country.</p><p>Bloomberg calls for three specific actions by congress: 1) pass the Fix Gun Checks Act, which would close the private-sale loophole that allows more than 40% of gun sales to go through without a background check; 2) pass an enforceable and effective assault weapons ban and a ban on high-capacity magazines; and 3) make gun trafficking a felony. </p><p>\"Last night the president said he would use whatever power his office holds to address this violence, and I think it's critical that he do so,\" Bloomberg said. \"We need immediate action... It should be at the top of their agenda.\"</p><!-- Guardian Watermark: internal-code/content/401234406|2012-12-22T11:49:03Z|d5af581e3160c1e6eb5ae9aaaa3ac2b0c60919c8 -->","showInRelatedContent":"true","lastModified":"2012-12-17T19:31:52Z","hasStoryPackage":"true","score":"1.0","secureThumbnail":"https://static-secure.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2012/12/17/1355772215340/New-York-City-mayor-Micha-005.jpg","standfirst":"• Mayor makes uncompromising call for action<br />• <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/us-news-blog/2012/dec/17/newtown-shootings-funerals-victims-live#block-50cf670f95cb356c029eb0b4\">Follow the day's news from Newtown here</a>","shortUrl":"http://gu.com/p/3ct86","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2012/12/17/1355772215340/New-York-City-mayor-Micha-005.jpg","wordcount":"364","commentable":"true","internalContentCode":"401234406","isPremoderated":"false","byline":"Tom McCarthy in New York","publication":"guardian.co.uk",